```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Unknown: Agent Registered

    Unknown --> Healthy: Ping Success (2xx/3xx)
    Unknown --> Degraded: 4xx Response
    Unknown --> Unhealthy: 5xx / Error / Timeout

    Healthy --> Healthy: Ping Success
    Healthy --> Degraded: 4xx Response
    Healthy --> Unhealthy: 5xx / Error / Timeout

    Degraded --> Healthy: Ping Success
    Degraded --> Unhealthy: 5xx / Error / Timeout

    Unhealthy --> Healthy: Ping Success (resets counter)
    Unhealthy --> Offline: Failures ≥ threshold (default: 3)

    Offline --> Healthy: Single Ping Success
    Offline --> Offline: Continued Failures

    note right of Unknown
        Initial state on registration
        No health check performed yet
    end note

    note right of Unhealthy
        Consecutive failure counter
        increments with each failure
    end note

    note right of Offline
        Hysteresis prevents state flapping
        Requires 3 consecutive failures
        Single success recovers
    end note
```

## States
- **Unknown**: Initial state, no health check performed
- **Healthy**: Last ping succeeded (2xx/3xx response)
- **Degraded**: 4xx responses received (service degraded but functional)
- **Unhealthy**: 5xx/connection error/timeout (failures counted)
- **Offline**: Consecutive failures exceeded threshold (default: 3)

## Transitions
- **Ping Success (2xx/3xx)**: Any Healthy or Degraded state maintained, Offline recovers
- **4xx Response**: Healthy → Degraded (service degraded)
- **5xx/Error/Timeout**: Healthy/Degraded → Unhealthy, Unhealthy counter increments
- **Failures ≥ threshold**: Unhealthy → Offline (hysteresis triggered)

## Guards
- **Failure counter resets**: On any Healthy/Degraded result
- **Offline promotion**: Only when consecutive failures reach threshold
- **Recovery from Offline**: Single successful ping (no waiting period)
